CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.User`
(
  UserId STRING NOT NULL,
  EmployeNumber STRING(50) NOT NULL,
  UserTypeId STRING NOT NULL,
  FormOfAddressId STRING,
  LastName STRING(100),
  FirstName STRING(100),
  MiddleName STRING(50),
  TitleId STRING,
  OfficePhone STRING(30),
  MobilePhone STRING(30),
  EmailAddress STRING(100) NOT NULL,
  PasscardId STRING(50),
  PasscardInternalId STRING(50),
  StartPageId STRING,
  Deleted BOOL NOT NULL,
  PrivacyPolicyAccepted BOOL NOT NULL,
  DisableNewUpdatePopup BOOL NOT NULL,
  PrivacyPolicyAcceptedDate TIMESTAMP,
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
